表係鬼。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_mailbox/131\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_mailbox%2F131&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=e0394127\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_mailbox/131</a><br />\n<br />\n7⃣94北角37歲梁義士，還押212日<br />\n<br />\n8⃣1209旺角18歲陳義士，被捕2次（831鐳射筆），還押116日<br />\n<br />\n9⃣1031深水埗20歲張義士還押155日。被逼戴裝逼拍照，被一拳毆腹部，被恐嚇「再唔講嘢就打你」<br />\n<br />\n1⃣0⃣1111青衣29歲蔡義士還押144日<br />\n<br />\n1⃣1⃣1112長沙灣19歲韓義士還押143日。狗車上被男殺人犯掌摑，辱罵「臭X」，恐嚇「信唔信我係度強姦你」<br />\n<br />\n1⃣2⃣1118旺角24歲黎義士還押137日<br />\n<br />\n1⃣3⃣1118理大大屠殺26歲温義士還押130日。被逼戴裝備拍照，被圍毆，禁止看醫生<br />\n<br />\n1⃣4⃣1118油麻地23歲梅義士<br />\n<br />\n1⃣5⃣1201旺角30歲梁義士還押94日<br />\n<br />\n詳情睇被捕組🙇&zwj;♀🙇&zwj;♀🙇&zwj;♀🙇&zwj;♀🙇&zwj;♀🙇&zwj;♀<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/13579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk%2F13579&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=5ed54aed\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/13579</a>"},{"pid":"f81c8e0a4c99660de83dc94bdab8094b404805da","tid":1956042,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ee69d0223643d6fce27ee12f01be9d900c5135","tid":1956042,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:31:02.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16219de35bf6fd266b1a1dd05548b367c7ae3859","tid":1956042,"uid":188864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:35:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"114119f8d85015cf29bd4ccfa39ad6ae0ece51ac","tid":